{
  "stem": "13623.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Some of us [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] believe what happened, and some of us don't want to believe what happened.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't-- I didn't think it happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't think it happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We ran into my father's younger brother, who came from a different city, in a different ghetto that we hadn't seen before for a few years.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We ran into him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we made up to meet him the following day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name is Abe Stern, who lives in Montreal today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We never saw him after that short meeting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A day or two later after we're in Auschwitz, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- they tell all kids 14 years and younger to sleep in the-- in the same barrack, but in a different part of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we didn't believe what happened to our parents and to-- and to our mothers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Instead of us hiding and trying to pass off for older, we just listened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we just did it, not knowing why they-- why they're asking us to do that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In fact, some of the people, the older people, tell us, you're going to be taken to your mothers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You will listen to your mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Make-- make sure that you don't give her a hard time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Tell your mother that we're OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They thought that they-- none of us knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As luck would have it, a day or two later, this law was rescinded.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because they made up a transport of people, and they needed so many bodies to send to some other place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't know where, but we're told that we will be going to another camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
